			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002066_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<!-- hand 01 41 top left--><!-- hand 02 63381 top right--><!-- hand 03 Livingstone top left-->
<lb/><p rend="center">Bath</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">18<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi><choice><abbr>Sept<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi></abbr><expan>September</expan></choice> 1864</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> Williamson</p>
<lb/><p>It gave me great 
<lb/>pleasure to <choice><sic>recieve</sic><corr>receive</corr></choice> a 
<lb/>letter from you 
<lb/>some time ago. 
<lb/>It was laid aside 
<lb/>to be answered but 
<lb/>I never have been 
<lb/>able. I now seize 
<lb/>a moment just 
<lb/>to say thank you 
<lb/>for I am in the throes getting ready 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002066_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>a speech to be delivered 
<lb/>this evening in the 
<lb/>theatre. I never 
<lb/>was intended for a 
<lb/>public speaker &amp; 
<lb/>never like to hear 
<lb/>myself speaking so 
<lb/>you may judge 
<lb/>I am not in a 
<lb/>proper frame of 
<lb/>mind for answering 
<lb/>a lady's letter</p>
<lb/><p>The limited time 
<lb/>I have to spend at 
<lb/>home &amp; some 
<lb/>work I have to do 
<lb/>prevent my 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002066_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<lb/>acceptance of your 
<lb/>very kind invitation 
<lb/>but I beg that 
<lb/>you will present 
<lb/>my warmest sal-î€€
               <!--hyphen on both lines-->utations to your 
<lb/>husband and our 
<lb/>young friend</p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone</p>
<lb/><p><!---added next day-->19<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> the speech was 
<lb/>got through somehow <gap extent="1" unit="lines" agent="damage"/>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002066_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'-->
<lb/>you but want of time 
<lb/>as I must work as 
<lb/>much as I can now 
<lb/>my steamer being out 
<lb/>at Bombay &amp; seven 
<lb/>black men waiting 
<lb/>for me. I know Sir 
<lb/>John Richardson &amp; 
<lb/>would be glad to meet him 
<lb/>anywhere. I have that 
<lb/>pleasure this evening 
<lb/>at D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Watson's.</p>
<lb/><p>Begging that you 
<lb/>will kindly excuse 
<lb/>me. I am &amp;c. <gap extent="1" unit="lines" agent="damage"/>
<lb/><!--signature cut off--></p>
			
